column2: SELECT #  petroR9#Err_g, petroR9#_g, petroR9#Err_r, petroR9#_r,  petroR9#Err_i, petroR9#_i, petroR5#Err_g, petroR5#_g,  petroR5#Err_r, petroR5#_r, petroR5#Err_i, petroR5#_i,  veldisp, veldisperr, mstellar_median, mstellar_err FROM PhotoObjall AS p  JOIN specobjall AS spec on spec.bestobjID = p.objid  JOIN stellarMassPCAWiscM1# AS s ON s.specobjid = spec.specobjid WHERE  petroR9#Err_g > # and petroR9#_g > #*petroR9#Err_g and  petroR9#Err_r > # and petroR9#_r > #*petroR9#Err_r and  petroR9#Err_i > # and petroR9#_i > #*petroR9#Err_i and  petroR5#Err_g > # and petroR5#_g > #*petroR5#Err_g and  petroR5#Err_r > # and petroR5#_r > #*petroR5#Err_r and  petroR5#Err_i > # and petroR5#_i > #*petroR5#Err_i and  petroR5#_g < # *petroR9#_g and petroR5#_g > #*petroR9#_g and  petroR5#_r<#*petroR9#_r and petroR5#_r>#*petroR9#_r and  petroR5#_i<#*petroR9#_i and petroR5#_i>#*petroR9#_i and  veldisperr ># and veldisp > #*veldisperr and  veldisp ># and veldisp < # and mstellar_err ># and   mstellar_median > #*mstellar_err
